Test "Simple bToken Transfer Not Allowed by Comptroller"
    NewComptroller
    ListedBToken ZRX bZRX initialExchangeRate:1e0
    Comptroller SetCollateralFactor bZRX 0.1
    EnterMarkets Geoff bZRX
    Prep Geoff Some ZRX bZRX
    Mint Geoff 50e18 bZRX
    -- Just to be sure, check initial balances
    Invariant Remains (Erc20 bZRX TokenBalance Geoff) (Exactly 50e18)
    Invariant Remains (Erc20 bZRX TokenBalance Torrey) Zero
    -- Just transfer
    AllowFailures
    Transfer Geoff Torrey 60e18 bZRX
    Assert Revert "revert insufficient liquidity"

Test "Simple bToken Transfer From"
    NewComptroller
    ListedBToken ZRX bZRX initialExchangeRate:1e9
    Prep Geoff Some ZRX bZRX
    Mint Geoff 50e18 bZRX
    -- Just to be sure, check initial balances
    Invariant Remains (Erc20 bZRX TokenBalance Torrey) Zero
    Assert Equal (Erc20 bZRX TokenBalance Geoff) (Exactly 50e9)
    Assert Equal (Erc20 bZRX TokenBalance Coburn) Zero
    -- Add approval
    From Geoff (Erc20 bZRX Approve Torrey 25e9)
    Assert Equal (Erc20 bZRX Allowance Geoff Torrey) (Exactly 25e9)
    -- Perform transfer from
    From Torrey (Erc20 bZRX TransferFrom Geoff Coburn 10e9)
    Assert Equal (Erc20 bZRX TokenBalance Geoff) (Exactly 40e9)
    Assert Equal (Erc20 bZRX TokenBalance Coburn) (Exactly 10e9)
    Assert Equal (Erc20 bZRX Allowance Geoff Torrey) (Exactly 15e9)

